{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_01_01",
  "title": "スペシャル\nライブ\n作戦会議",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、作戦会議を始めましょうか\nさくらちゃん、琴乃ちゃん、報告してくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's start the strategy meeting.\nSakura-chan‚ Kotono-chan‚ could you give us your reports?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.2144900322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんにお願いして\nリズノワも計画に参加してくれることになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked Rio-san to do it‚\nand LizNoir will also participate in the plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "endTime": 13.45,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルの三人も喜んで協力するって言ってくれたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The three from TRINITYAiLE also said they'd be happy to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6355099678,
      "endTime": 17.9462807655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスも事情を話したら\n特別に歌ってもいいと言ってくれたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I explained the situation to IIIX‚\nthey reluctantly agreed to sing as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1355099678,
      "endTime": 23.0654647827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、渋々って感じだったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it seemed more like they did it unwillingly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2688433011,
      "endTime": 26.438389714499998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "これで星見プロのアイドル全員参加決定だね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With this‚ all the idols from Hoshimi Prods. will participate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6355099678,
      "endTime": 30.8809295177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "お世話になってる人達に日頃の感謝を伝えるって話が\n随分大事になりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems that the idea of expressing gratitude to those\nwho have been taking care of us has become quite important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0688433011,
      "endTime": 37.90884326290001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "感謝の気持ちを表すために、スペシャルライブを\nやろうって最初に言い出したのは誰だったっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who was it that first suggested we should hold a special live concert\nto express our gratitude?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0943532308,
      "endTime": 44.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピと月ストのみんなで話してたら、アイドルらしく\n歌で感謝を伝えたいって話になったのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "While Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest were talking‚\nit naturally came up that we wanted to convey our gratitude through song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9825640996,
      "endTime": 52.3563055356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "誰がというより、自然にみんながそうしたいと\n思ったんじゃないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rather than who suggested it‚\nI think everyone just naturally felt that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5492307663,
      "endTime": 57.6800246238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもお世話になってる三枝さん、さとみさん\nそれに{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To Saegusa-san and Satomi-san‚ who always take care of us‚\nand also to {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8825640996,
      "endTime": 64.09671386080001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに感謝を伝えるスペシャルライブ\n絶対成功させようね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's make the special live concert\nto express our gratitude a success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.349229749,
      "endTime": 69.2282998402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "問題は会場と音響スタッフさんをどうするかだけど……\n私達だけで全部手配出来るかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The problem is‚ what should we do about the venue and the sound staff…\nCan we arrange everything ourselves?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4158964157,
      "endTime": 77.9907491684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "そういうのはいつも\n{user}さんに任せてたからね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've always\nleft that kind of thing to {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1762591362,
      "endTime": 82.5996603012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんだけど\n会場の準備は私に任せてもらえないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of that‚\ncould I be in charge of preparing the venue?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.8095924695,
      "endTime": 88.1197510084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "実は何年か前に、事務所に内緒でライブをやりたくて\n会場を借りようとしたことがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ a few years ago‚ I secretly wanted to hold a live‚\nso I tried to rent the venue without the agency's knowledge.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3095924695,
      "endTime": 95.6470756848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "結局ライブは実現しなかったけど……あそこなら\n事情を話せばステージを使わせてくれると思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live concert never happened in the end‚ but…\nif I explain the situation‚ I think they'll let us use the stage there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8429258029,
      "endTime": 103.5722909609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\nそちらの手配は遙子さんにお任せします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood.\nI'll leave the arrangements to you‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7762591362,
      "endTime": 108.2662591933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "それからセトリなんだけど……\n各グループのセンター五人で歌ってほしい曲があるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ about the setlist…\nI want the centers out of each five groups to sing a particular song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4517691612,
      "endTime": 115.89224538799999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "五人で歌ってほしいって、どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sing with the center five people? What does that mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0851024945,
      "endTime": 120.05163310360001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……まずはその曲がどうやって生まれたか\n話しておきましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… first‚\nlet's talk about how that song came to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2517691612,
      "endTime": 126.8171204566,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9348.233127599997
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数年前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few years ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.6851045291,
      "endTime": 128.8517691612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃん？　表情が暗いけど、何かあった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-chan? You look down‚ something up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7184297245,
      "endTime": 135.1559128445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-02.m4a",
      "text": "それが、私のドキュメンタリーを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ they asked me to",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3517630578,
      "endTime": 137.96667683910002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "作ることになったんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "make a documentary about me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9666768391,
      "endTime": 140.3995996475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ～、ドキュメンタリーなんて凄いじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Woww‚ a documentary‚ that's impressive!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5851096153,
      "endTime": 144.6221618175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-01.m4a",
      "text": "と言っても配信用の短い動画なんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just a short video for streaming‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8184429486,
      "endTime": 148.364482208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "それで、さっきまでインタビューを受けてたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I was interviewed until a moment ago‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.364482208,
      "endTime": 152.0995864232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "話しながら、デビューしてからどんなことがあったか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "talking about what happened since my debut‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.285096391,
      "endTime": 156.35136182189999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
