      "translations": {
        "en": "I have neither popularity nor talent…\nI'll just end up dragging you down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.7183351196,
      "endTime": 307.0910561241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-26.m4a",
      "text": "私の曲を私と一緒に歌うのは嫌ってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't want to sing my songs with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 307.2850017862,
      "endTime": 310.99049923539997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だったらオリジナルの曲にする。それならいいでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then let's make it an original song. That should be fine‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.9904992354,
      "endTime": 315.6661361056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-07.m4a",
      "text": "正式なライブじゃなくて、私の曲でもなかったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's not an official live‚ and it's not my song either‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.8516460734,
      "endTime": 319.8339580913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-05.m4a",
      "text": "何も問題ないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "there shouldn't be any problem‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 319.8339580913,
      "endTime": 322.1994551974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……そうなるのかしら……\nでも、だからって、やるとは一言も言って――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that's… Is that how it's going to be?\nBut even so‚ I didn't say I'd do it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.3849651652,
      "endTime": 330.9599315959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-05.m4a",
      "text": "決まりだね！　私達の感謝の気持ちを込めた",
      "translations": {
